resources.string: Every Android application published on Google Play has a unique package id. So before creating a new application one should check if the package id is available. This screen helps you to check if your package id is free to use.
This package id is already taken!
This screen is Feature Module. Also it uses ViewModel with LiveData, dagger for DI and logic is in another Kotlin Multi Platform module. Ktor is used for network requests.
Package id should be longer than %d symbols
